snippet.title: Terra Foliata - Official Announcement Trailer 2024
snippet.description:
Explore the Valley of Mists, where dreams create reality. Study people's dreams and determine their fate. Leave the hectic world for a while and return to yourself.

Developed by Teleolabs, Terra Foliata is coming to PC in 2025. It's available to wishlist now on Steam: store.steampowered.com/app/2927540/Terra_Foliata
